        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2270943294" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer1598777035254855095">There&apos;s a lifeforce in Thomas Wolfe&apos;s writing, a gusto and relish for the vitality of language that spills out of the gloriously verbose sentences and sing-song dialog of the characters. Flavours, sounds; textures and tones are all described in delicious and vivid detail. It moves along in an undulating rhythmic pace like the seasons in the story. A beautiful joy of a book.</span>
  <span id="freeText1598777035254855095" style="display:none">There's a lifeforce in Thomas Wolfe's writing, a gusto and relish for the vitality of language that spills out of the gloriously verbose sentences and sing-song dialog of the characters. Flavours, sounds; textures and tones are all described in delicious and vivid detail. It moves along in an undulating rhythmic pace like the seasons in the story. A beautiful joy of a book.</span>
